CatDescriptText: Related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 13, 1965, pg. 7 reads: "D.I.'s in Costume - Adding their own personal glamour to their Mardi Gras Ball, held last Sunday night at the Hilton Hotel, were D.I. members (left to right) Margaret Watson, Mildred Connors, Birdie Dunlap, Juanita Drake, Nellye Barron Gloria Grate and Alberta Thompson. - Harris Photo"
TitMainTitle: Members of D. I. club wearing costumes, from left: Margaret Watson, Mildred Connors, Birdie Dunlap, Juanita Drake, Nellye Barron, Gloria Golden Grate, and Alberta Thompson standing in front of King's Garden room of Hilton Hotel for D. I.'s Mardi Gras Ball
